edu.uga.dawgtrades.model

Interface Bid

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable

    public interface Bid
extends Persistable
    This interface represents a Bid placed by a RegisteredUser on an Auction. The It has a collection of methods to read/write Bid's attributes. It also extends the Persistable interface, since objects of this class will be stored in the persistent data store.
